Defines a simple box called "Sea of Clouds - Tweet" and includes some css.

*INSTALL*

1. Download the jquery.tweet.js via: https://github.com/seaofclouds/tweet

2. Take the /tweet folder that is inside your uncompressed download or clone and put into root of module folder (tweet_seaofclouds)

3. Enable & Put blog where you wants

4. customize the drupal.tweet.js & the css in /tweet

5. wait until I do better admin for this

*MORE INFO*
http://tweet.seaofclouds.com/
